title: Ludwick Community Center Dodgeball
description: Indoor court. Come join for some casual dodgeball fun. Meet inside the main gym of the Ludwick Community Center. Games start as soon as enough players arrive.
schedule: Thursdays at 5:00 PM and Sundays at 2:30 PM

title: Damon Garcia Field Ultimate
description: Outdoor field. Join us for friendly, casual games of ultimate frisbee. All skill levels are welcome. Meet on the grassy fields at Damon Garcia Sports Complex.

title: SLO Pickup Ultimate
description: Outdoor fields. Join us for friendly, casual games of ultimate frisbee. All skill levels are welcome. Meet on the Lower Sport Complex at Cal Poly. Games start as soon as there are enough numbers.

title: SLO Run Club
description: Social Run Club! All skill levels encouraged. Schedule released monthly, meetups at a different brewery on Wednesdays, and a different coffee shop on Saturdays!

title: SLO Pickleball
description: French Park! Casual and more competitive play! Come out and hang! Other social events too. Please come out!
schedule: Seven days a week, 8:00 AM to dusk, first come first serve basis.

title: SLO Pickleball
description: Meadow Park! Recreational and beginner play! Other social events too! Come out and hang!
schedule: Monday-Friday, 9:00AM to 11:30AM, first come first serve basis.

title: SLO Pickleball + Tennis
description: French Park Lower Courts! Casual and more competitive play! Come out and hang! Other social events too. Please come out!
schedule: Tuesdays and Wednesdays, 8:00 AM to 12:00PM, first come first serve basis.
